juniEthernetAgent.name: juniEthernetAgent

revisions.description: Juniper-ETHERNET-MIB: Added Ethernet interface statistics support.
Juniper-ETHERNET-MIB: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
Juniper-ETHERNET-MIB: Added MAU type and length support.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniEthernetAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Ethernet component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniEthernetAgentV1.name: juniEthernetAgentV1
juniEthernetAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Ethernet component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Ethernet component was supported in JUNOSe 2.x system
        releases.
juniEthernetAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Ethernet application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when VLAN support was add.

juniEthernetAgentV2.name: juniEthernetAgentV2
juniEthernetAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Ethernet component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Ethernet component was supported in JUNOSe 3.x system
        releases.
juniEthernetAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Ethernet application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when VLAN stack support was added.

juniEthernetAgentV3.name: juniEthernetAgentV3
juniEthernetAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the Ethernet component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Ethernet component was supported in JUNOSe 4.0 system
        releases.
juniEthernetAgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Ethernet application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when VLAN stack support was added.

juniEthernetAgentV4.name: juniEthernetAgentV4
juniEthernetAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the Ethernet component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Ethernet component was supported in JUNOSe 4.1 through
        5.1 system releases.
juniEthernetAgentV4.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Ethernet application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when Ethernet interface statistics support was added.

juniEthernetAgentV5.name: juniEthernetAgentV5
juniEthernetAgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the Ethernet component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Ethernet component is supported in JUNOSe 5.2 and
        subsequent system releases.
juniEthernetAgentV5.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Ethernet application in JUNOSe.
